# Handy commands

* `findview` - i.e. `findview "color " | sort | uniq` - will find a string across all view files within the directory
* `findviewr` - i.e. `findviewr "#404040" "#112233"` - will find and replace the first string with the second one
* `findjs` - i.e `findjs "Invalid fields"` - will find the string in JavaScript files
